General.Name: TomCo Energy Plc
General.Description: TomCo Energy Plc engages in the oil shale exploration and evaluation activities primarily in the United Kingdom and the United States. It holds 100% interests in nine oil shale leases covering approximately 15,488 acres located in Uintah County, Utah. The company is based in Douglas, the Isle of Man.
General.Address: Sixty Circular Road, Douglas, Isle of Man, IM1 1AE
